    "302906": {
        "Desc": "Talk to The Balladeer",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Look at that, hot on my heels. You know, you didn't have to cut your catch-up short just to keep me company. Oh, but I guess you panicked when you realized that I might enter Irminsul ahead of you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Nahida sent me to babysit you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Shut your beak, jailbird! No way a prisoner gets to be so smug!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "I understand that prisoners have to put up with harassment from the guards, but right now, I'm on temporary release, so maybe you should think about backing off a little."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Sounds like a successful rendezvous."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "I need to be quite clear about something. In a few moments, you'll be entering into the innermost region of Irminsul. It is an environment like no other, and the most important place in all of Sumeru."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Unlike anywhere else, Irminsul's inner region consists exclusively of torrents of information. You must put aside your differences and be extremely careful as you navigate your way through."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "I know there are many grievances between you on both sides, but it is essential that you remain calm after entry. This is as much for your own safety as anything else."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...Understood."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Fine, let's call a truce, but only until this mission's over..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Let's cut each other a little slack, shall we? We are gonna be traveling together, after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Per my agreement with Lesser Lord Kusanali, I'll be at the front. It's my job to lead the way and get rid of any obstacles in our path. All you have to do is keep your pretty eyes open and try not to fall behind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ha! You sure are confident, Paimon'll give you that. You make it sound like you're even more experienced at adventuring than us!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "If there are no further objections, I suggest we get going."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Or did you need some time to mentally prepare yourselves?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You...! Ugh! The snark on this guy! It's unbearable!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There's no need for all the biting sarcasm."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Focus on doing your job."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "...Hmph."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "We can start now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Irminsul access granted. Initiating connection procedure..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Is this a small sapling?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Argh, darn it! C'mon, let's catch up with him!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "302917": {
        "Desc": "Talk to The Balladeer",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "302907": {
        "Desc": "Talk to The Balladeer",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow... So this is the inside of Irminsul..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's different than what I imagined..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ohh... Paimon's never seen anything like this. And it feels like a sacred place..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Irminsul is closely intertwined with the entirety of Teyvat. Every bit of information flowing here means something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Pick your jaws up off the floor. It's time to go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why is it that Paimon just wants to do the opposite of everything he says..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Lesser Lord Kusanali, we will now proceed to the heart of Irminsul."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Can you still sense where the heart of Irminsul is?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Yes. Permission to begin searching for information there?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nahida",
                    "T": "Permission granted. Go ahead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Let's go. Stay close, don't go running off."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, so... say we did go running off in here, what would happen?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whâ€”What are you smirking at?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "I was just imagining the look on your travel companion's face if you went and got lost."
                },
                {
                    "N": "The Balladeer",
                    "T": "Anything's possible in here â€” you can't rule anything out. So if you wanna stay safe, your best option is to stick close to me."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
